          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The keyword arguments start, stop and step are used by calling slice(start, stop, step). This implies axis_slice() does not handle its arguments the exactly the same as indexing. To select a single index k, for example, use     axis_slice(a, start=k, stop=k+1) In this case, the length of the axis 'axis' in the result will be 1; the trivial dimension is not removed. (Use numpy.squeeze() to remove trivial axes.)"
            }
